{% extends "base.html.twig" %}

{% block title %}IWF Career Mode - Build Your Legend | Online Wrestling Game{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<div class="container mx-auto p-4">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="text-center py-16">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6">Dominate the Ring in IWF Career Mode</h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">Start as a Level 1 rookie and forge your path to the Hall of Fame. Create your custom wrestler, train their attributes, learn devastating new moves, and challenge for championships in the ultimate online wrestling career experience.</p>
        <a href="{{ base_url }}career" class="shiny-cta inline-block font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-full text-xl uppercase tracking-wide"><span>Start Your Career</span></a>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Grid -->
    <section class="py-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Feature 1: Create Your Prospect -->
            <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-yellow-400 mb-4">1. Create Your Unique Prospect</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-300">Your journey begins here. Define your wrestler's name, size, and look from a selection of unique avatars. Will you be a towering giant, a high-flying daredevil, or a technical mastermind? Your legend is a blank canvas.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Feature 2: Level Up & Evolve -->
            <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-yellow-400 mb-4">2. Level Up and Evolve</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-300">Compete in matches to earn XP and Gold. With each level, you'll earn Attribute Points (AP) to enhance your wrestler's Strength, Toughness, and more. Spend your gold at the Training Center to build a custom moveset that fits your style.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Feature 3: Choose Your Archetype -->
            <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-yellow-400 mb-4">3. Define Your Destiny</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-300">At Level 5, make a permanent choice that will shape your career. Select an Archetype—Brawler, Technician, High-Flyer, or Powerhouse—to gain powerful, permanent bonuses that enhance your natural abilities.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

     <!-- How It Works Section -->
    <section class="py-16 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-12">Your Path to Greatness</h2>
        <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <!-- Timeline Line -->
            <div class="absolute left-1/2 h-full w-0.5 bg-gray-700 -translate-x-1/2"></div>
            
            <!-- Step 1 -->
            <div class="relative mb-12 flex items-center w-full">
                <div class="w-1/2 pr-8 text-right">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-400">The Grind (Levels 1-30)</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 mt-2">Earn your stripes by taking on a variety of opponents. Focus on earning Gold and AP to build a solid foundation for your attributes and learn crucial new moves.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute left-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 rounded-full -translate-x-1/2 border-4 border-gray-900"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2 -->
             <div class="relative mb-12 flex items-center w-full">
                <div class="w-1/2"></div>
                <div class="w-1/2 pl-8 text-left">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400">The Main Event (Levels 31-60)</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 mt-2">You're a contender. Hire a legendary manager to boost your earnings and stats. Challenge other players' prospects in the Challenge Zone to prove you're the best.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute left-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-full -translate-x-1/2 border-4 border-gray-900"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 3 -->
            <div class="relative mb-12 flex items-center w-full">
                <div class="w-1/2 pr-8 text-right">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-400">The Legend (Levels 61-100)</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 mt-2">This is where legends are made. Compete in high-stakes tournaments for massive gold prizes and cement your legacy. At Level 100, retire your prospect to the Hall of Fame, adding them to the game as a permanent, formidable opponent for all future careers.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute left-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-yellow-500 rounded-full -translate-x-1/2 border-4 border-gray-900"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
{% endblock %}
